    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://xp-song.github.io/authors/xpsong/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://xp-song.github.io/authors/xpsong/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello, my name is Xiao Ping (XP). I&amp;rsquo;m an environmental researcher and educator, with experience in interdisciplinary projects involving scientists, designers and city planners. Broadly speaking, my &lt;a href=&#34;https://xp-song.github.io/academia/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;research&lt;/a&gt; seeks to improve the social and ecological performance of urban greenery. As an educator, my &lt;a href=&#34;https://xp-song.github.io/academia/#teaching&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;teaching&lt;/a&gt; covers topics ranging from statistical computing and geospatial analysis, to &lt;a href=&#34;https://xp-song.github.io/music/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;music&lt;/a&gt;. I&amp;rsquo;m a big fan of R. Outside of work, I enjoy playing the drums and going for adventure sports. Feel free to contact me via &lt;a href=&#34;#contact&#34;&gt;email&lt;/a&gt; or on social media if you&amp;rsquo;re interested to connect!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
